  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 41f6666ec8adc1846b1cc0f2bf100762, type: 2}
  delayBetweenMessages: 2
  lines:
  - "Heard from quite a few people that apparently they know more about the symptoms
    the virus produces than they\u2019re willing to share. "
  - 'Sounds a bit fishy but I trust they have good reason for doing so. '
  - "I have my scepticisms about them but, they\u2019ve never given me reason to
    properly believe in them. Don\u2019t you think?"
  bridgeAfterMessages: 1
  bridgeResponse1: "Well\u2026 They let my family live happily, and pursue our dreams,
    so I have no real problem with them."
